(1) Seventh Ave., south from West 44th Street, and showing the southern portion of Times Square, with the Times Building separating Broadway from Seventh Ave. The buildings shown on the right (west side), and starting with the Paramount south to West 42nd Street, bear Broadway numbers, but actually are on Seventh Ave.

1936.

W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Writers Project.

(2) Another view, and not showing the Times Building.

1936.

W. P. A. Photo.
Federal Writers Project.
